HEADWORD: Standardize
<hw>Stand"ard*ize</hw> <pr>(-⟦imac⟧z)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>To reduce to a normal standard; to calculate or
adjust the strength of, by means of, and for uses in,
analysis.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

